            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head/>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"The Black Republican papers have been circulating the following: 'Who
                    settled Virginia? John Smith. Who unsettled Virginia? John Brown.' The author of
                    this wonderful witty production, doubtless, thought he had 'got off a good
                    thing;' but a Southern editor asks in reply: 'Who settled John Brown?
                    Virginia!'"</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary/>
                <note/>
